    "ethical issues, plagiarism, etc.).",
    "The dialog with GPT-4 as a validation of its own performance retrospectively in autumn 2023 confirmed the test results in general, but also found more in-depth reasons responsible for the capabilities of GPT-4 in handling this exam so well.",
